300159571.Title: Whirlpool 18 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in Stainless Steel, Silver
300159571.Description: Always find a place for your fresh and frozen goods inside this Whirlpool 28 in. top-freezer refrigerator. It offers convenient storage options between its 18 cu. ft. capacity and spacious FLEXI-SLIDE bin, which moves horizontally to accommodate tall items. Bright LED interior lighting casts a natural light on the contents of your black, white or stainless steel top-freezer refrigerator, giving your food the spotlight. Plus, you can add the Whirlpool EZ Connect icemaker kit for easily-accessible ice.
